   295	    serialized result (or error) on ``queue``. Top-level so it can be
   296	    pickled by the 'spawn' start method on macOS.
   297	
   298	    Error-kind dispatch matters: the parent translates 'gmsh_error' to
   299	    GmshMeshGenerationError (user-geometry fault → 422), but every
   300	    backend/setup fault must surface as something OTHER than
   301	    GmshMeshGenerationError so the pipeline routes it as 5xx. Codex
